	a) Added a new mode of fund delivery to micro enterprises, to wit:   	“Provision of guarantees to loans granted by the banks to qualified P3   	beneficiaries”, aside from direct lending and wholesale lending to 	conduits which shall on-lend to micro enterprises;
      b)  Changed the percentage of total loans disbursed from “twenty percent  	(20%)” to “ten percent (10%)” which shall be provided to SB Corp. to 	support its administrative and operating expenses; and added a 	statement that the said amount will “be sourced from the earnings of the 	P3 Fund.”;

