	In addition, an amount equivalent to the loan provisioning and guarantee calls in the past year shall be allocated annually to the P3 Fund.”</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp-•	Reported out by CSBED on March 21, 2018 as substitute HB 7446 under Committee Report No. 683
